cross: Cymbidium Lambert Day x Cymbidium Karen Hawaiian

measurements.description: Forty-four round flowers and five buds on three arching inflorescences up to 74cm long; sepals and petals burnt umber, darker veins, more prominent mid-line; lip orange-yellow overlaid maroon along edge, dark maroon blotches and spots, dark maroon line centrally; column orange-yellow spotted maroon, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
